leaflet.desc: An open-source JavaScript library for mobile-friendly interactive maps

proj4leaflet.desc: Full Projection and CRS support in Leaflet

proj4.desc: Proj4js is a JavaScript library to transform point coordinates from one coordinate system to another, including datum transformations.

openlayers.desc: OpenLayers 3 is a high-performance, feature-packed library for creating interactive maps on the web.

woodman.desc: Flexible JavaScript logger utility based on log4j. Runs client-side and server-side.

sortable.desc: Sortable is a minimalist JavaScript library for reorderable drag-and-drop lists on modern browsers and touch devices. No jQuery.
